# Welcome to your Gemini capsule

This is a freshly-deployed Gemini capsule, running on the openhost-gemini
app (backed by agate). It is serving the default index file bundled
with the image.

=> /about.gmi About this capsule
=> /editing.gmi How to edit these pages

## Gemini in 10 seconds

Gemini is a lightweight internet protocol, simpler than the web. Each
page is plain text with a tiny bit of markup (gemtext):

* Lines starting with `#` are headings (one to three levels).
* Lines starting with `=>` are links.
* Lines starting with `*` are bullet list items.
* Lines starting with `>` are blockquotes.
* Lines starting with ``` toggle a preformatted block.
* Everything else is a paragraph.

That's the whole language.

